So we are pigs,
pigs in the blanket, ja?

303
00:18:43,845 --> 00:18:45,154
-Ja.
-Ja.

304
00:18:45,221 --> 00:18:47,490
-This is funny then, ja?
-Ja, ja.

305
00:18:47,556 --> 00:18:48,702
-This is funny.
-Ja.

306
00:18:48,773 --> 00:18:51,391
-Yep, that's a good one.
-Good night, everyone.

307
00:18:51,460 --> 00:18:54,275
-It's time for lights out.
-We can't go to sleep yet.

308
00:18:54,340 --> 00:18:56,642
We haven't heard a bedtime story. Right?

309
00:18:56,708 --> 00:18:57,689
Shrek, yeah!

310
00:18:59,300 --> 00:19:01,188
All right. All right.

