00:19:41,089 --> 00:19:44,438
This place is worse
than I thought... feared.

325
00:19:44,513 --> 00:19:47,612
So he grabbed up his belly
and screwed up his face

326
00:19:47,681 --> 00:19:48,729
And let loose a...

327
